**Choose Kive if you:**

âœ… Need to support both cloud and local deployments  
âœ… Want to switch memory providers without code changes  
âœ… Need multi-tenancy and context isolation built-in  
âœ… Want a simple, unified API across 10+ providers  
âœ… Prefer to focus on building AI apps, not memory infrastructure  

